_sText:
This map is a very early beta! Please dont blame me if you find bugs ;-D

----------------------
MAP INFORMATION:
----------------------

Map Name: ze_28weeks_betaV01b
Map Type: ze (Zombie Escape)
Release date: January 4th, 2010
Available Weapons: Standard 
Map Environment: City
Map's Time of Day: Day and night 
Special Features: many locations
Recommended/Maximum Players: 20-64
Custom Textures Used: yes (but only one)
Custom Sounds Used: no
.NAV File Included (for bots and locations): no
Tips for this Map: Tell me everything you want. (Ofc only about the map... (-; )


----------------------
INSTALLATION      :
----------------------

Place it in steam/steamapps/youraccountname/counterstrikesource/cstrike/maps folder.
Servers need the Zombie Mod Plugin!
